PrecisAuthority to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Province of NEW BRUNSWICK and the FARM CREDIT CORPORATION in order to provide financial assistance, in the form of interest-free loans, to potato and other horticultural crop producers in New Brunswick who were affected by drought or blight in 1994.
